commit.message:
Makefile.in: Make .lo the target of compilation.

2001-10-02  Toon Moene  <toon@moene.indiv.nluug.nl>

	* libF77/Makefile.in: Make .lo the target of compilation.
	* libI77/Makefile.in: Ditto.
	* libU77/Makefile.in: Ditto.

From-SVN: r45964

files.patch:

+2001-10-02  Toon Moene  <toon@moene.indiv.nluug.nl>
+
+	* libF77/Makefile.in: Make .lo the target of compilation.

+	* libU77/Makefile.in: Ditto.
